#: ../../language/error_codes/E4195.md:1
msgid "E4195"
msgstr "E4195"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4195.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `invalid_where_clause_field`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`invalid_where_clause_field`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4195.md:5
msgid ""
"A `where` clause accepts only the fields that are meaningful for that "
"context. For a function contract, use fields such as `proof_require`, "
"`proof_ensure`, `proof_decrease`, `proof_axiomatized`, and "
"`proof_reasoning`. For a loop contract, use fields such as "
"`proof_invariant`, `proof_yield`, and `proof_reasoning`."
msgstr ""
"`where` 子句只接受当前上下文中有意义的字段。对于函数契约，请使用 "
"`proof_require`、`proof_ensure`、`proof_decrease`、`proof_axiomatized` 和 "
"`proof_reasoning` 等字段。对于循环契约，请使用 `proof_invariant`、"
"`proof_yield` 和 `proof_reasoning` 等字段。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4195.md:11
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4195.md:13
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"fn keep(x : Int) -> Int where { proof_note: x >= 0 } {\n"
"  x\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  ignore(keep)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4195.md:17
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4195.md:19
msgid "Replace the unknown field with a supported `where` clause field."
msgstr "将未知字段替换为支持的 `where` 子句字段。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4195.md:21
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"fn keep(\n"
"  x : Int,\n"
") -> Int where {\n"
"  proof_require: x >= 0,\n"
"  proof_ensure: result => result == x,\n"
"  proof_reasoning: \"The function returns its argument unchanged.\",\n"
"} {\n"
"  x\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  inspect(keep(1), content=\"1\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

